column5: If you're just starting or finishing your day...hope it's a good one...I think it's going to be a little warm so don't overexert yourself...take the day and go fishing  Maureen
Mornin Moe & everyone else, it's gonna be a fine day indeed !!
Good Morning Mo, Lew and the rest of the earlybirds! It's gonna be a warm one here, but that's the way I like it!!!!
Good Morning. Yup calling for a warm one today so everyone enjoy.
Good morning early birds... its gonna be a nice day here too and I'm off work at noon today...  Off to look at MORE boats....lol

Hello and good morning to everyone!  I really don't know why I'm up this early  Woke up about 2 hours ago and couldn't get back to sleep so I figured why not play a couple of games on the 'puter and drop into OFC.  I think it's going to warm back up again, we had about a week of really great weather with warm days and cool evenings, perfect!  But it sure looks like were going back into a humid warm cycle again.  Maybe I can make a couple of phone calls this morning and then if nothing is happening with my customer list I'll head out to fish too.  Good Day to everyone
If you think its going to be hot today....wait until Sunday. Supposed to be 35 PLUS the humidex!  Yikes!
